        public Note(int dynamic,
    int articulation,
    int pitchClass,
    int octave,
    int offset)
        Builds a Note from VMF codes.
        Parameters:
        dynamic - The VMF code for the dynamic.
        articulation - The VMF code for the articulation.
        pitchClass - The VMF code for the pitch class.
        octave - The octave of this note.
        offset - The offset from the beginning of the previous note. In the case of the first note of the piece, this is from the beginning of the music.
